value: Breeds chiefly from southeastern Europe and western Mediterranean lands north and east across Asia to Transbaikalia, and the upper Amur, south to Persia, the Himalayas and southwestern China. Winters in the southern half of its breeding range and to the Nile Valley; India and south- ern China.
